            "value": "<p>This <em>+1 resilient </em>studded leather is adorned with colorful sequins that sparkle in even the faintest light.</p>\n<p>While wearing the spangled rider's suit, you gain a +2 item bonus to Command an Animal you are riding.</p>\n<p>Any animal you ride automatically knows the Drop Prone and Step basic actions, in addition to any other basic actions it knows (normally only Leap, Seek, Stand, Stride, and Strike).</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">R</span> (move)</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You take damage while mounted or your mount Drops Prone</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You dismount, moving off your mount into a space adjacent to it.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 item bonus to Command an Animal you are riding</li>\n</ul>"
